{
  "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "把一个物块挂在弹簧上，拉开再松手，它会来回振动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "但现实里没有永动，空气和摩擦会不断偷走能量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.34,
      "size": 21456,
      "text": "这种带阻力的振动，就叫阻尼振荡。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "zeta",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "zeta-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/zeta-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.43,
      "size": 38880,
      "text": "运动方程写成 m x撇撇 加 c x撇 加 k x 等于 0。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "zeta",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "zeta-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/zeta-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "我们定义阻尼比 ζ 等于 c 除以二倍根号 m k。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "zeta",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "zeta-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/zeta-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25056,
      "text": "一个 ζ 的取值，就决定了整个振动的命运。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "under",
      "line_id": "und-1",
      "filename": "under-und-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/under-und-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "当 ζ 小于 1，阻力较弱，物块仍会来回穿越平衡点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "under",
      "line_id": "und-2",
      "filename": "under-und-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/under-und-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "但每一次摆幅都比上一次小，包络线是一条指数衰减曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "under",
      "line_id": "und-3",
      "filename": "under-und-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/under-und-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "这就是欠阻尼：振荡着，却慢慢平息下来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "critover",
      "line_id": "co-1",
      "filename": "critover-co-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/critover-co-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.58,
      "size": 41328,
      "text": "当 ζ 恰好等于 1，是临界阻尼：不再振荡，且以最快速度回到平衡。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "critover",
      "line_id": "co-2",
      "filename": "critover-co-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/critover-co-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.51,
      "size": 40176,
      "text": "当 ζ 大于 1，是过阻尼：同样不振荡，却因阻力过大而回得更慢。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "critover",
      "line_id": "co-3",
      "filename": "critover-co-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/critover-co-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "汽车悬挂追求临界附近，既不颠簸，又能迅速稳住。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "试着切换不同的阻尼比，观察曲线形态的转变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "看欠阻尼的波浪，如何在临界处被彻底抹平。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "同一个方程，靠阻尼比 ζ 分出三种截然不同的命运。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "欠阻尼振荡衰减，临界最快回位，过阻尼缓慢归零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "damped-oscillation",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/damped-oscillation/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "一个参数掌控全局，这正是微分方程的魅力，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
